sparqlUpdate

@Doc(value="SPARQL update query")
void sparqlUpdate(@Par(name="query",type="SPARQL update query",desc="e.g. INSERT INTO { GRAPH $usercontext$ { s p o } }",isRequired=true)
                      java.lang.String query)
                  throws java.rmi.RemoteException,
                         java.lang.Exception
Perform a SPARQL 1.1 Update query (e.g. INSERT, DELETE, UPDATE). If the query contains the special variable $usercontext$, it is replaced with an new user context. In such case also the meta context information are written.
